{"tid":1628661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衛生署 : 若出現呼吸道感染病徵，應戴上口罩並盡早求醫。","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:26:35.000Z","uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9ebc0c5d7e8df4a7a61a78e43a78e25e13939930","tid":1628661,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:05:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191005/s00001/1570283712272/2%e6%ad%b2%e7%ab%a5%e6%9f%93%e4%be%b5%e5%85%a5%e6%80%a7%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e7%90%83%e8%8f%8c%e4%ba%a1-%e5%8f%af%e9%a3%9b%e6%b2%ab%e5%82%b3%e6%92%ad%e8%a1%9b%e7%bd%b2%e7%b1%b2%e7%8f%be%e7%97%85%e5%be%b5%e5%8d%b3%e6%88%b4%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191005%2Fs00001%2F1570283712272%2F2%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e7%25ab%25a5%25e6%259f%2593%25e4%25be%25b5%25e5%2585%25a5%25e6%2580%25a7%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e7%2590%2583%25e8%258f%258c%25e4%25ba%25a1-%25e5%258f%25af%25e9%25a3%259b%25e6%25b2%25ab%25e5%2582%25b3%25e6%2592%25ad%25e8%25a1%259b%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e7%25b1%25b2%25e7%258f%25be%25e7%2597%2585%25e5%25be%25b5%25e5%258d%25b3%25e6%2588%25b4%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfELM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=ac414777\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191005%2Fs00001%2F1570283712272%2F2%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e7%25ab%25a5%25e6%259f%2593%25e4%25be%25b5%25e5%2585%25a5%25e6%2580%25a7%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e7%2590%2583%25e8%258f%258c%25e4%25ba%25a1-%25e5%258f%25af%25e9%25a3%259b%25e6%25b2%25ab%25e5%2582%25b3%25e6%2592%25ad%25e8%25a1%259b%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e7%25b1%25b2%25e7%258f%25be%25e7%2597%2585%25e5%25be%25b5%25e5%258d%25b3%25e6%2588%25b4%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9&h=46d8df03\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191005/s00001/1570283712272/2%e6%ad%b2%e7%ab%a5%e6%9f%93%e4%be%b5%e5%85%a5%e6%80%a7%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e7%90%83%e8%8f%8c%e4%ba%a1-%e5%8f%af%e9%a3%9b%e6%b2%ab%e5%82%b3%e6%92%ad%e8%a1%9b%e7%bd%b2%e7%b1%b2%e7%8f%be%e7%97%85%e5%be%b5%e5%8d%b3%e6%88%b4%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9</a><br />\n一名2歲男童感染侵入性肺炎球菌致嚴重肺炎，出現病徵4天後不治，是今年首宗死亡個案。衛生署衛生防護中心指出，肺炎球菌主要經病人咳嗽和打噴嚏而產生的飛沫、與病人親密接觸或觸摸被病菌污染的物件而傳播，呼籲市民若出現呼吸道感染病徵，應戴上口罩並盡早求醫。<br />\n<br />\n該男童過往健康良好，9月29日出現發燒、咳嗽及呼吸困難等病徵，10月2日被帶到威爾斯親王醫院急症室求醫，同日入住該院兒童深切治療部，其後情況轉壞，至10月3日不治。其血液樣本對肺炎鏈球菌呈陽性反應，臨牀診斷為嚴重肺炎。他潛伏期內沒有外遊，家居接觸者至今無出現病徵。衛生防護中心正調查男童有無接種肺炎球菌疫苗；個案將轉交死因裁判官調查。<br />\n連同這宗個案，今年至今共有29宗侵入性肺炎球菌感染個案，其中一人死亡。"},{"pid":"7e09ca49063c2fffa710525584906e76eae08acf","tid":1628661,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6fa0635f77013d88c41a2dfc42d4cc4c648f9e","tid":1628661,"uid":64469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:26:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思想重推！麻煩入一入黎睇下你既角色定位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［我有野講］咪撚再唱歌叫口號［入黎睇下自己衰咩］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612280</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}